So you won’t bear it if I ever die.

SAYLOR
(voice is cracking)
Shut up.  Don’t say that.  Never mention this possibility.  Please.

RICK
I see...  So, you trust me, right?...

SAYLOR
(beginning to cry)
Yeah.  Yeah, I do.

RICK hugs SAYLOR.

SAYLOR (CONT’D)
(crying)
I love you as the best friend.  I don’t want to lose you.  Don’t make the nightmare happen.  Don’t make this universe a terrible place.

RICK
Saylor.  Don’t worry.  I’ll look after myself.  I’ll try my best.

SAYLOR
(crying)
You better do.

