But why does Lisa keep an eye on you specifically, anyway?

RICK
I wonder...  Maybe it’s strange, but if we exclude the version that I’m the weakest link, can the robots have... an affection?

EDDIE
Nonsense.  It must be something pragmatic.  AI doesn’t have feelings, it merely emulates them.  It is just a roleplay, an algorithm.

SHIRLEY
(to EDDIE)
This is not as wild as you think.  You saw that she has a mind of her own.
(generally)
Even if she’s electronic, she has emotions.  She has traits.  She has opinions.  Ultimately, she’s an artificial human, half-digital.  This is not AI as we know it.  I’m more curious about where she came from.  Saylor?  *You* are important to her.  Why?

SAYLOR
Honestly, no idea.  It’s like she came out of nowhere.  She’s been following me since 2024, downloading herself into my devices.  But the only reason she explained her motives was that... I’m a person pleasant to do business with?

