SHIRLEY
Best friend.  Best friends take care of each other better than family and relatives.

SAYLOR
Right...  He could be called my brother, actually.

RICK
Best sister in the universe.

RICK claps SAYLOR on the shoulder.

SHIRLEY
See?

SAYLOR
Point taken.

