### Draft #1  •  End of Part 2

[[29 August 2024]]

SHIRLEY
Stop it.  And Rick.  I’m glad you keep her grounded.  With her explosive personality - no offense, Saylor - you’re a perfect counterbalance.

SAYLOR
I mean, you’re right.

RICK
You’re really kind, Shirley.  Thank you.  Also, you read my mind like an open book.  Yes, I feel it’s my duty to help Saylor watch her steps.

EDDIE
It is.  I can understand.

SHIRLEY
He helps me so I don’t get carried too far away.

SAYLOR
Like I never know when something can go wrong, huh, Rick?

RICK
Sometimes you can be too confident to the point of blindness.  Just like... all of us?

SAYLOR
Admittedly, sometimes confidence is a curse.

RICK
Here we go.

